---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="River of Life is an Apostolic Pentecostal church in Henry, IL. Where life begins - a loving community dedicated to serving people on their spiritual journey.">
  <PageHero title="About River of Life" image="/hero/1.jpg" />

  <section class="content">
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>River of Life is an Apostolic Pentecostal church and a loving community of Christ-followers dedicated to serving people on their spiritual journey. We exist to help people find and follow Jesus. Whether you're exploring faith for the first time or have been walking with God for years, there's a place for you here.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <p>When you visit River of Life, you'll find a friendly, welcoming atmosphere. Our services include contemporary worship music and practical, Bible-based teaching. We have programs for kids and students so the whole family can grow together.</p>
      <p>Come as you are - there's no dress code. We'd love to meet you!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Service Times</h2>
      <div class="service-times-list">
        <div class="service-item">
          <span class="service-time">10:00 AM</span>
          <span class="service-name">Sunday Christian Education</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
          <span class="service-time">11:00 AM</span>
          <span class="service-name">Sunday Main Service</span>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
          <span class="service-time">7:00 PM</span>
          <span class="service-name">Wednesday Bible Study</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Location</h2>
      <p>425 University Ave<br />Henry, IL 61537</p>
      <p><a href="tel:+13093643165">(309) 364-3165</a></p>
      <a href="/directions" class="btn">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7zm0 9.5c-1.38 0-2.5-1.12-2.5-2.5s1.12-2.5 2.5-2.5 2.5 1.12 2.5 2.5-1.12 2.5-2.5 2.5z"/></svg>
        Get Directions
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h2>Meet Our Pastor</h2>
      <p>Get to know the pastor who leads River of Life.</p>
      <a href="/pastor" class="btn">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z"/></svg>
        Meet Pastor Andrew
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .service-times-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .service-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold);
  }

  .service-name {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-navy);
  }

  .service-time {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-teal);
    min-width: 5rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 3rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>
